message: Dear Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product, which is valued at $8,000 to both you and myself. Considering its high quality and unique benefits, I would like to propose a fair deal of $7,200 for this exceptional item. This price not only ensures a valuable transaction for you but also allows me to maintain a reasonable profit margin. I believe we can reach an agreement that satisfies both of our needs. Looking forward to your positive response.
